profile__tracking__message:
This feature tracks your location at all times. This data can be useful for healthcare professionals to track cases of COVID-19 even if you forget to log your meetings or visits.

Sharing this data with us is completely optional. We understand that this is very sensitive and we go to great lengths to protect your data.
